  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Defining Project Scope**\n\nOkay, I\'m focusing on scoping out this e-commerce project. My priority is to clearly define the MVP\'s scope: traditional Algerian handicrafts and clothing. This will be an e-commerce website. I\'m prioritizing elements and functionalities needed for a basic product showcase and sales platform. Currently, I\'m thinking of focusing on core features to keep the scope manageable.\n\n\n**Expanding Feature Set**\n\nI\'m now expanding the feature set. I\'ve considered rent-or-buy options for the products, alongside a clean seller dashboard for inventory management. Order fulfillment is a priority, and I\'m planning a mock payment gateway integration \342\200\223 a React-based frontend simulation. The goal is an interactive visualization of the checkout process, including cart, renting/buying choices, shipping, and mock card payments, all culminating in a seller dashboard view. I plan to use Figma for UI/UX.\n\n\n**Refining Technical Choices**\n\nI\'m now refining the technical choices. With the focus being a React-based frontend simulation, I\'m leaning toward minimizing complexity. Considering it\'s a mock payment gateway integration, I\'m thinking of using `localStorage` for data persistence. This approach keeps the prototype simple, focusing on the UI/UX visualization rather than backend complexity.\n\n\n**Evaluating Feature Relevance**\n\nOkay, I\'m now evaluating feature relevance and eliminating unwanted functionality. I\'ve ruled out `firebase-integration` and `oauth-integration` as unnecessary for this mock project. I\'ve flagged `image-generation` as relevant, recognizing the need for visually appealing product imagery, and will explore the potential for generating sample images or using placeholders. I will NOT use `shadcn-ui`.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will perform a quick check of our skills and read the instructions for image generation to ensure we can provide Algerian traditional visuals for our e-commerce prototype."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 581103447
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
