  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Crafting Initial Data**\n\nI\'m now generating `/src/data.ts` to hold an initial dataset. I\'m focusing on Algerian traditional crafts and clothing, specifically integrating detailed imagery URLs, captivating descriptions, and pricing in DZD. I aim for a robust, visually appealing product representation.\n\n\n**Defining Item Properties**\n\nI\'m now detailing item properties like pricing in Algerian Dinars, and enabling both rental and purchase options for clothing and jewelry, but buying only for handicrafts. I\'ve defined four outstanding traditional Algerian items: the Karakou of Algiers, the Chedda of Tlemcen, the Traditional Kabyle Dress, and Zellij Hand-Painted tiles. I\'ve defined buying and renting prices.\n\n\n**Adding More Product Details**\n\nI\'m expanding the data with more handcrafted goods. I\'ve included a ceramic vase, a copper teaset, a Berber rug, and a silver Kabyle brooch. I\'ve detailed pricing, stock levels, origins, and categories. Each item has its unique attributes and values for purchase and rent where applicable, with origins in Tlemcen, Constantine, Ghardaia, and Kabylie, respectively.\n\n\n**Sourcing Product Imagery**\n\nI\'m now integrating visuals for the expanded product list, focusing on high-quality images. I\'m prioritizing Unsplash for its reliability and aesthetic fit, using curated keys to ensure culturally appropriate visuals. I\'m sourcing high-resolution images for the Karakou, Chedda, and traditional rug, aiming for captivating and accurate product representations. I\'m making sure these images do not look broken.\n\n\n**Refining Image Integration**\n\nI\'m now integrating visuals for the expanded product list, focusing on high-quality images. I\'ve sourced Unsplash URLs for each item, prioritizing elegant and high-class visuals. I\'ve carefully selected URLs for a black and gold velvet Karakou dress, a Chedda of Tlemcen, a Kabyle dress, traditional ceramics, a copper teaset, and a traditional rug, ensuring they represent the items well. I\'m making sure these images do not look broken.\n\n\n**Enhancing Image Assets**\n\nI\'m now integrating visuals for the newly added items. I\'m focusing on generated images via the `generate_image` tool for enhanced asset quality. I\'ve decided to create four high-resolution PNG images: `karakou_clothing.png` (a modern Karakou jacket), `chedda_tlemcen.png` (a traditional Chedda dress), an `algerian_ceramic.png` and a new `berber_carpet.png`. I aim for photorealistic representations. I\'m excited by this approach.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now generate 4 highly customized, beautiful visual assets representing traditional Algerian clothing and crafts using the `generate_image` tool. This will give our e-commerce MVP prototype a premium appearance. Here is the first generation for the Algiers Karakou."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 10
      nanos: 722709047
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
