    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/components/CheckoutModal.tsx`. This component handles the complete payment gateway simulation tailored specifically for Algeria\'s absolute real payment methods (**CIB card managed by SATIM** and **EDAHABIA card managed by Alg\303\251rie Poste**). It also includes a client-side visual credit card mockup that changes themes/logos on-the-fly and handles date duration choices for clothing rentals."
